Kubernetes Dashboard Setup on AWS EC2 (kubeadm Cluster
Environment
This setup assumes the following environment:

AWS EC2 Instances
├── k8s-master
├── k8s-worker1

Kubernetes Installation
├── kubeadm
├── containerd/docker
Step 1: Verify Cluster Health
Login to the Kubernetes Master Node.

kubectl get nodes
Expected Output:

NAME         STATUS
k8s-master   Ready
k8s-worker1  Ready
